_description: This file stores detailed chart data used for visualization, export, and sharing during integration testing. It contains the complete chart data in a format suitable for rendering by chart visualization libraries and frontend components.
_instructions: This file is automatically updated by the integration test. DO NOT modify manually.

charts._description: Collection of astrological charts with complete visualization data. Includes both original and rectified charts.
charts._usage: Used by the frontend to render detailed interactive chart wheels with all astrological elements properly positioned.

items._description: This is a template structure for chart visualization data. Actual charts will be populated during testing.

visualization_data._description: Technical data needed to visualize the chart as a wheel diagram

wheel_data._description: Positional data for rendering the chart wheel

outer_wheel._description: Zodiac signs displayed in the outer ring of the chart

middle_wheel._description: House cusps displayed in the middle ring of the chart

inner_wheel._description: Planets displayed in the inner area of the chart

export_formats._description: Available export formats for the chart

comparison_data._description: Data for chart comparison visualizations. Contains paired charts with difference analysis.
comparison_data._usage: Used by the frontend to display side-by-side or overlay comparisons between original and rectified charts.

items._description: This is a template structure for comparison visualization data. Actual comparisons will be populated during testing.

visualization_data._description: Technical data needed to visualize the chart comparison

differences._description: Calculated differences between the two charts

export_formats._description: Available export formats for the comparison
